    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300053438_49_16421-16510",
      "chapterUid": 49,
      "range": "16421-16510",
      "markText": "周灭商后，人祭被周人消除，但周人并未开创一种新的宗教，而是采用世俗的人文主义立场，与极端宗教行为保持距离，不允许其干预现实生活，所谓“敬鬼神而远之”。这奠定了后世中国的文化基础。",
      "totalCount": 14910,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300053438&chapterUid=49&rangeStart=16421&rangeEnd=16510",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7b032ae0813ab7b5fg0180c0?chapterUid=49&rangeStart=16421&rangeEnd=16510"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300053438_78_4272-4293",
      "chapterUid": 78,
      "range": "4272-4293",
      "markText": "也许，人不应当凝视深渊；虽然深渊就在那里。",
      "totalCount": 11843,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300053438&chapterUid=78&rangeStart=4272&rangeEnd=4293",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7b032ae0813ab7b5fg0180c0?chapterUid=78&rangeStart=4272&rangeEnd=4293"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300053438_49_18967-19014",
      "chapterUid": 49,
      "range": "18967-19014",
      "markText": "也许，我们至今也还难以完全了解我们自己。考古，就犹如一面深埋地下的镜子，倒映出我们陌生的形象。",
      "totalCount": 8028,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300053438&chapterUid=49&rangeStart=18967&rangeEnd=19014",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7b032ae0813ab7b5fg0180c0?chapterUid=49&rangeStart=18967&rangeEnd=19014"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300053438_77_760-819",
      "chapterUid": 77,
      "range": "760-819",
      "markText": "在三千年前的古人类文明中，只有华夏独自走出了神权的掌控，成为一个“异类”。这是一种过于早熟的世俗文明，一直持续到今日。",
      "totalCount": 7530,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300053438&chapterUid=77&rangeStart=760&rangeEnd=819",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7b032ae0813ab7b5fg0180c0?chapterUid=77&rangeStart=760&rangeEnd=819"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300053438_52_8419-8469",
      "chapterUid": 52,
      "range": "8419-8469",
      "markText": "从发表的一张照片看，至少三枚人头骨集中在一起，还有多根大腿骨被从股骨头部位截断，可能是敲骨吸髓所致。",
      "totalCount": 6307,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300053438&chapterUid=52&rangeStart=8419&rangeEnd=8469",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7b032ae0813ab7b5fg0180c0?chapterUid=52&rangeStart=8419&rangeEnd=8469"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300053438_49_17567-17621",
